snippet.title: Slender Man Caught on Camera #5

localized.description: The Following video shows the REAL Slender Man. Watch at your own risk. I knew I couldn't leave that truck out there from the previous tape so I went back out there not much happens until the end. In the next video my friend will come to the woods with me so he can see what I have been seeing.
